q01q:`Do I need an internet connection?`,q01a:`Only for installation and the first model download. Once Ollama and a model are installed, Nox works fully offline.`,
q02q:`Do I need a powerful GPU?`,q02a:`A CUDA-capable GPU is recommended for fast speech recognition and AI responses. Nox also works in CPU mode, but the voice pipeline and responses will be slower.`,
q03q:`Which AI models work?`,q03a:`All models supported by Ollama: Llama 3.1, Mistral, Phi-3, Qwen, CodeLlama and more. You can switch models anytime in settings.`,
